FBIS4-32125 "dreeu119_c_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Russian Debt-Repayment Agreement Signed Russian Debt-Repayment Agreement Signed LD2006201294 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network in Czech 1900 GMT 20 Jun 94 LD2006201294 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network Czech BFN [Text] Czech Deputy Finance Minister Vladimir Rudlovcak has signed a Czech-Russian intergovernmental agreement in Moscow. The agreement concerns the Russian debt to the Czech Republic in the amount of $3.5 billion that Russia should repay by 2003. The Czech Republic will receive $52 million this year, $101 million next year, and $301.9 million in 1996.
